      <title>科里·布克（Cory Booker）打破了最长的参议院演讲的记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-04-01/ap-newsalert-cory-booker-breaks-the-record-for-longest-senate-speech-previously-held-by-segregationist-strom-thurmond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（AP）＆Mdash;科里·布克（Cory Booker）打破了最长的参议院演讲的记录，此前由种族隔离主义者斯特罗姆·瑟蒙德（Strom Thurmond）持有。]]></description>
