    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚敦促大学将研究多样化。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/australia-urges-universities-to-diversify-research-away-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚外交部长潘妮·黄（Penny Wong）敦促大学在特朗普政府削减该部门的资金威胁之后，与美国境外的合作伙伴寻求更大的研究合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/australia-urges-universities-to-diversify-research-away-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:12:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两党参议员小组重新制定新的制裁，以袭击俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/bipartisan-group-of-senators-readies-new-sanctions-to-hit-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）拒绝与乌克兰进行善意的停火谈判或违反最终协议，则有50名共和党和民主党参议员提出了制裁计划，以打击俄罗斯和购买石油的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/bipartisan-group-of-senators-readies-new-sanctions-to-hit-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 22:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在周三会议上权衡蒂克托克出售计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-to-weigh-plans-for-tiktok-sale-at-meeting-on-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统将在周三开会，以考虑一项提案，该提案将蒂克托克（Tiktok）的美国业务从中国母公司Bytedance Ltd.撤离，这是据熟悉此事的人们的说法，在出售流行的社交媒体应用程序的截止日期之前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-to-weigh-plans-for-tiktok-sale-at-meeting-on-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 22:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着伊朗紧张局势的增加，五角大楼将第二号航空公司送往中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/pentagon-sends-second-carrier-to-mideast-as-iran-tensions-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）下令向中东（包括卡尔·文森（Carl Vinson）罢工集团和飞机）提供更多部队，因为美国誓言继续对伊朗支持的胡希叛军进行罢工，随着与德黑兰的紧张局势在核计划中的紧张局势不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/pentagon-sends-second-carrier-to-mideast-as-iran-tensions-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 21:31:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普罢工与道格·埃霍夫（Doug Emhoff）的律师事务所威尔基（Willkie）打交道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-strikes-deal-with-willkie-law-firm-home-to-doug-emhoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Willkie Farr＆amp;唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周二表示，加拉格尔（Gallagher）至少要承诺与“保守派理想”保持一致的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-strikes-deal-with-willkie-law-firm-home-to-doug-emhoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 20:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守派集团向律师事务所寻求免费帮助，并指出特朗普的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/conservative-group-solicits-free-aid-from-big-law-amid-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个与遗产基金会有联系的团体正在寻求利用唐纳德·特朗普总统针对律师事务所的行政行动的洪流，以获得保守派事业的免费法律帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/conservative-group-solicits-free-aid-from-big-law-amid-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 19:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NYC主计长将特斯拉套装推入股票养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/musk-s-doge-work-is-hurting-shareholders-nyc-comptroller-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市审计长布拉德·兰德（Brad Lander）正在推动该市对特斯拉公司提起股东诉讼，并指控汽车制造商错误地宣布了埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）在特朗普政府的工作有多少使他离开了公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/musk-s-doge-work-is-hurting-shareholders-nyc-comptroller-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 17:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贸易办公室针对魁北克的法语法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-trade-office-takes-aim-at-quebec-s-french-language-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国以魁北克有争议的法语法作为贸易的障碍，这一举动可能会使加拿大对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税做出反应的决定更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-trade-office-takes-aim-at-quebec-s-french-language-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 15:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
