      <title>康奈尔学生活动家战斗驱逐出境使我们离开了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/cornell-student-activist-fighting-deportation-has-left-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康奈尔大学（Cornell University）的一名研究生激进主义者是特朗普政府驱逐出境的目标，他说，他失去了阻止他的撤职后自愿离开该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/cornell-student-activist-fighting-deportation-has-left-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 14:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
